<div id='message'>
<p>Use zero for midnight</p>
</div>
<div id='explanation'>
<p>Since <a href="http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/rss/rssChangeNotes.html#111102Dw">11 November 2002</a>, the correct range for <a href="http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/rss/skipHoursDays.html#skiphours">skipHours</a> is 0 to 23.</p>
</div>
<div id='solution'>
<p>Replace the <code>24</code> with a <code>0</code>.</p>
</div>
